channel.title: How do I delete an Object?
channel.description:
How do i delete an object?
it's a closed chest i want to add a NPC there ( I know how to do that).
but I need help deleting the object that is in the way.
can any one help me? :confused: :| :confused:

item.title: How do I delete an Object?
item.dc:creator: @gamma gamma
item.description:
@gamma wrote:

[quote=“monkey money30, post:3, topic:252481”][quote author=chassy13 link=topic=333454.msg2598481#msg2598481 date=1230098114]

deleteThatObject()

[/quote]

oh yes, very very well explained… umm… well first of all for some reason I can not find the reason why I can not delete the object, I can’t seem to find it in Client.Java. the coords are X2850, Y3593 but there not in the client.java…

but then again when I searched a statue’s coords it worked. And i could remove them…

I just can’t remove the chest Curse that chest![/quote]

He means the deleteObject void smart one…
